    	    </stability>
	    <notes>
    		- Fixed typo in constant name (APN_PODUCTION -> APN_PRODUCTION)
    		- Incorrect warning message in apn_feedback()
    		- Added "invalid token" warning in apn_send()
    		- TSRM fixes
    	    </notes>
	</release>
	<release>
    	    <version>
		<date></date>
